          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2016-02-22</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Protecting Our Security Through Utilizing Right-Sized End-Strengths Act of 2016 or the POSTURE Act of 2016</strong></p> <p>This bill expresses the sense of Congress that given the uncertain world and the need for trained and ready U.S. land forces, the planned drawdown of land forces should cease.</p> <p>The bill sets forth:</p> <ul> <li> Army, Marine Corps, and Selected Reserve strength levels as of September 30, 2016; and</li> <li>Army, Navy, Marine Corps, and Air Force permanent active duty end strength minimum levels.</li> </ul>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-02-25T16:20:56Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
